The paper discusses the architecture and selection of blockchain technology for decentralized applications, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). It also covers data management and software engineering aspects, which could be classified under distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), software engineering (cs.SE), and databases (cs.DB). Additionally, the paper mentions insurtech, which could be related to cybernetics (cs.CY).
